   Crime activist Yusuf Abramjee tweeted a video of a hijacking at Twist Street in Albertville, Johannesburg. He said the driver was taken hostage during the crime. Video: Twitter
  
 
“The case of hijacking was opened at Sophiatown police station, the victim was dropped in Soweto with no injuries,” he said.
Makhubele said the car had yet to be recovered and police were yet to make any arrests.
Saturday Star